ailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33326,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/31\/fasting-ashura-9th-muharram\/","url_meta":{"origin":7435,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on &#8216;Ashura: Fasting day of &#8216;Ashura with 9th of Muharram","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 31, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Hakam ibn al-A\u2019raj reported: I went to Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, and I said, \u201cTell me about fasting the day of 'Ashura.\u201d Ibn Abbas said, \u201cWhen you see the crescent of the month of al-Muharram, count the days and wake up to fast on the ninth\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12186,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/02\/14\/ibn-wahb-fiqh-malik-layth\/","url_meta":{"origin":7435,"position":4},"title":"Ibn Wahb on Fiqh: I would be led astray, if not for Imam Malik","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 14, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Dhahabi reported: Ibn Wahb, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cWere it not for Malik and Al-Layth, I would have been ruined. I used to believe that everything narrated about the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, should be acted upon.\u201d Source:\u00a0Siyar A\u02bbla\u0304m al-Nubala\u0304\u02bc 8\/148 Ibn Abi Layla\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{